        {
            "title": "NBA｜火箭大炒爵士 落實事隔5年重返季後賽",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3472640c0a53bd3973e7d97debf7f89a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040314533258975.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">火箭落實重返季後賽。AP</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>火箭於周三NBA主場以143:105大炒爵士後，宣布鎖定今季季後賽資格，自2020年後重返季後賽，同時落實成為西南分區冠軍。賽後，火箭將帥都表示非常高興，其中D布魯士更矢言他們並不滿足於此。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/997cf7d580b834f3a1b27763f7ac4d66/2025-04/2025-04-03T024408Z_1291827723_MT1USATODAY25833020_RTRMADP_3_NBA-UTAH-JAZZ-AT-HOUSTON-ROCKETS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccf9bc85a8058ce49e8e331587290560/2025-04/2025-04-03T023907Z_254802272_MT1USATODAY25832994_RTRMADP_3_NBA-UTAH-JAZZ-AT-HOUSTON-ROCKETS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b8efc5c335800b15201f3f4e7ddb3ec9/2025-04/Jazz_Rockets_Basketball_60283--a06e5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/33cc8cd71401d40572ae57b0ff68d1e1/2025-04/Jazz_Rockets_Basketball_71613--11856.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a14657082dc99e1dabf3682feeda9cd2/2025-04/Jazz_Rockets_Basketball_08996--2b43c.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5a4b6f392fcb68edeacd5be16b743cad/2025-04/Jazz_Rockets_Basketball_02912--3f8fd.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a144de2e0cbd039bc4f1f7c8d15999e/2025-04/Jazz_Rockets_Basketball_78016--62bc5.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/288def4d101fc52bdd1c466fb3407294/2025-04/Jazz_Rockets_Basketball_34818--af794.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        火箭落實重返季後賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>火箭取得季後賽資格</h2>\n<p>除了第1節比數咬緊，火箭之後一直領放並愈拉愈遠，一度領先多達41分。最終，火箭在全隊共有7名球員攻入最少11分下，主場以143:105大炒爵士。賽後，火箭以50勝27負排西岸次席，落實鎖定今季季後賽資格，將自2019至2020球季後首次打入季後賽，另外他們亦落實成為西南分區冠軍。\n\n</p><h2>將帥大感高興</h2>\n<p>賽後，火箭主帥烏度卡喜言：「重回季後賽的感覺很好。對那些從沒打過季後賽的球員而言，這是一個很好的成績。事實上，從上賽季的基礎上進步，打入季後賽就是我們今季的目標。我們做了應做的事，現在重點是保持住。」而今場攻入21分的D布魯士就矢言：「我們很開心能打入季後賽，但是我們並不滿足於此。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2061886/即時-體育-NBA-火箭大炒爵士-落實事隔5年重返季後賽",
